ygData.messageBody:
Hi all,<br>I am new to the list and wanted to say
hi. I also wanted to tell everyone about my new site,
Behind EQ. Its a site for the players, not the game, of
Everquest. On the site you can read profiles that players
have submitted about themselves. It has every server
and players can also submit their own profiles. The
URL is <a href=http://www.behindeq.com. target=new>http://www.behindeq.com.</a> Please visit the
site. Thanks and I'll talk to ya soon!
